8&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-03.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-03.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-03.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-03.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-03.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-03.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></button><button aria-label=\"View image 4: KVRN Heavyweight Sweatpants — worn, Stone colorway\" aria-current=\"false\" class=\"relative flex-shrink-0 w-[68px] h-[90px] overflow-hidden bg-[var(--color-bg-raised)] transition-all duration-150 opacity-50 hover:opacity-80\"><img alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"68px\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fsweatpants-stone-04.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></button></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div><p class=\"kvrn-label mb-2\">KVRN</p><h1 class=\"text-[28px] md:text-[34px] font-light leading-tight tracking-tight\">Heavyweight Sweatpants</h1><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-3 mt-3\"><p class=\"text-[20px] font-light\">$250</p><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">USD, incl. tax</p></div></div><div class=\"kvrn-rule\"></div><fieldset class=\"border-0 p-0 m-0\"><legend class=\"sr-only\">Select color</legend><p class=\"label-11 mb-3\">Color<span class=\"normal-case tracking-normal ml-2 text-kvrn-text font-light\">— <!-- -->Stone</span></p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\" role=\"radiogroup\" aria-label=\"Product color\"><label title=\"Stone\" class=\"relative cursor-pointer group\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"Stone\" name=\"color\" checked=\"\" value=\"stone\"/><span class=\"block w-6 h-6 rounded-full border transition-all duration-150 border-transparent ring-2 ring-kvrn-text ring-offset-2 ring-offset-kvrn-bg\" style=\"background-color:#C4B49A\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></label><label title=\"Slate\" class=\"relative cursor-pointer group\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"Slate\" name=\"color\" value=\"slate\"/><span class=\"block w-6 h-6 rounded-full border transition-all duration-150 border-transparent group-hover:ring-1 group-hover:ring-kvrn-border-strong group-hover:ring-offset-1 group-hover:ring-offset-kvrn-bg\" style=\"background-color:#5C6470\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></label><label title=\"Off White\" class=\"relative cursor-pointer group\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"Off White\" name=\"color\" value=\"off-white\"/><span class=\"block w-6 h-6 rounded-full border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border group-hover:ring-1 group-hover:ring-kvrn-border-strong group-hover:ring-offset-1 group-hover:ring-offset-kvrn-bg\" style=\"background-color:#EDE8E0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></label><label title=\"Washed Black\" class=\"relative cursor-pointer group\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"Washed Black\" name=\"color\" value=\"washed-black\"/><span class=\"block w-6 h-6 rounded-full border transition-all duration-150 border-transparent group-hover:ring-1 group-hover:ring-kvrn-border-strong group-hover:ring-offset-1 group-hover:ring-offset-kvrn-bg\" style=\"background-color:#2A2A2A\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></label></div></fieldset><div class=\"kvrn-rule\"></div><div><fieldset id=\"size-selector\" class=\"border-0 p-0 m-0\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><legend class=\"label-11\">Size</legend><a class=\"text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text tracking-wide underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"#size-guide\">Size guide</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\" role=\"radiogroup\" aria-label=\"Select size\" aria-required=\"true\"><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"XS\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"XS\" name=\"size\" value=\"xs\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">XS</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"S\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"S\" name=\"size\" value=\"s\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">S</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"M\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"M\" name=\"size\" value=\"m\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">M</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"L\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"L\" name=\"size\" value=\"l\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">L</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"XL\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"XL\" name=\"size\" value=\"xl\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">XL</span></label><label class=\"relative cursor-pointer\" title=\"XXL\"><input type=\"radio\" class=\"sr-only\" aria-label=\"XXL\" name=\"size\" value=\"xxl\"/><span class=\"flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 text-[11px] font-light tracking-widest border transition-all duration-150 border-kvrn-border text-kvrn-text hover:border-kvrn-border-strong\" aria-hidden=\"true\">XXL</span></label></div></fieldset><p class=\"text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-3\">Wide-leg, sits at natural waist. True to size.</p></div><div class=\"kvrn-rule\"></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-kvrn-text text-kvrn-bg border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-[#333333] hover:border-[#333333] active:bg-black active:border-black disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-[56px] px-9 text-[13px] w-full\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">Add to bag — $250</span></button><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\" aria-label=\"Express checkout\"><button class=\"h-12 border border-[var(--color-border)] text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-all duration-150\" aria-label=\" Pay — available at checkout\" disabled=\"\" title=\"Available at checkout\"> Pay</button><button class=\"h-12 border border-[var(--color-border)] text-[12px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:border-[var(--color-border-strong)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-all duration-150\" aria-label=\"G Pay — available at checkout\" disabled=\"\" title=\"Available at checkout\">G Pay</button></div></div><ul class=\"space-y-2.5\" aria-label=\"Shipping and returns\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 13 13\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6.5l3 3 6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Ships in 3–5 business days</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 13 13\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6.5l3 3 6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Free returns within 30 days</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\"><svg width=\"13\" height=\"13\" viewBox=\"0 0 13 13\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 6.5l3 3 6-6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Tracked delivery on every order</li></ul><div class=\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border border-t border-kvrn-border\"><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-construction\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Construction<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-construction\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-construction\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-5\"><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1\">400 GSM+ Fleece</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Same triple-brushed loopback terry as the hoodie. Consistent weight across the full system.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1\">Wide-Leg Silhouette</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Proportioned deliberately — wide enough to carry structural presence, tapered enough at the ankle to stay precise.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1\">Concealed Drawcord</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Elastic waistband with internal drawcord. Adjustable, invisible from the exterior.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] mb-1\">Back Zip Pocket</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Single back pocket with concealed YKK zip at the seam. Secure. Seamless with the garment exterior.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-specifications\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Specifications<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-specifications\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-specifications\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><dl class=\"space-y-2.5\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Material</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">100% ring-spun combed cotton</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Weight</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">400 GSM+</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Construction</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Loopback terry, triple-brushed interior</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Waist</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Elastic with internal drawcord</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Pockets</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Two side pockets, one back zip pocket</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Leg</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Wide-leg, tapered at ankle</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Branding</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">None visible</dd></div><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><dt class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] min-w-[110px] flex-shrink-0\">Care</dt><dd class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Machine wash cold, inside out. Air dry.</dd></div></dl></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-shipping\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Shipping<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-shipping\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-shipping\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\"><p><span class=\"text-[var(--color-text)]\">USA Standard</span> — 5–7 business days, $8</p><p><span class=\"text-[var(--color-text)]\">USA Express</span> — 2–3 business days, $18</p><p><span class=\"text-[var(--color-text)]\">International</span> — 7–14 business days, from $22</p><p class=\"pt-2\">Orders before 1pm EST ship same day. Tracked delivery included.</p></div></div></div></div><div><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"accordion-returns\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between py-4 text-[13px] font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase text-left hover:text-kvrn-muted transition-colors duration-150 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-kvrn-text\">Returns<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ml-4 flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 relative\"><span class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-current -translate-y-1/2\"></span><span class=\"absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-1/2 w-px bg-current -translate-x-1/2 transition-transform duration-300\"></span></span></button><div id=\"accordion-returns\" role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"accordion-trigger-returns\" class=\"overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-out max-h-0 opacity-0\"><div class=\"pb-6 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\"><div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\"><p>30-day returns on unworn, unwashed items with original tags attached.</p><p>Email <a href=\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\" class=\"text-[var(--color-text)] underline underline-offset-2\">hello@kvrn.com</a> with your order number to initiate. Prepaid label for US returns.</p><p>Refunds processed within 5–10 business days of receipt.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"mt-20 md:mt-32 pt-12 md:pt-16 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\" aria-labelledby=\"pdp-construction\"><p id=\"pdp-construction\" class=\"kvrn-label mb-8 md:mb-12\">Construction</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4\"><div class=\"border border-[var(--color-border)] p-5 md:p-6 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\">400 GSM+ Fleece</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Same triple-brushed loopback terry as the hoodie. Consistent weight across the full system.</p></div><div class=\"border border-[var(--color-border)] p-5 md:p-6 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\">Wide-Leg Silhouette</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Proportioned deliberately — wide enough to carry structural presence, tapered enough at the ankle to stay precise.</p></div><div class=\"border border-[var(--color-border)] p-5 md:p-6 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\">Concealed Drawcord</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Elastic waistband with internal drawcord. Adjustable, invisible from the exterior.</p></div><div class=\"border border-[var(--color-border)] p-5 md:p-6 space-y-3\"><p class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.12em] uppercase\">Back Zip Pocket</p><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed\">Single back pocket with concealed YKK zip at the seam. Secure. Seamless with the garment exterior.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"mt-20 md:mt-32 pt-12 md:pt-16 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]\" aria-labelledby=\"complete-set\"><p id=\"complete-set\" class=\"kvrn-label mb-8 md:mb-12\">Complete the set</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 items-center max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[3/4] bg-[var(--color-bg-raised)] overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"K